\[BP^2 + CP^2 = AB^2 + AC^2 + 2AP^2 - 2AP (AB \cos \angle BAP + AC \cos \angle CAP).\]Since $\angle BAP + \angle CAP = \angle BAC,$
\[BP^2 + CP^2 = AB^2 + AC^2 + 2AP^2 - 2AP (AB \cos \angle BAP + AC \cos (180^\circ - \angle BAP)).\]Then
